OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy night with patchy rain or
OL,7,Fshowers, the showers occasionally
OL,8,Fheavy around western coasts. Winds
OL,9,Fwill be brisk, and strong at times
OL,10,Faround western coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,13,Fscattered showers. Turning brighter
OL,14,Fthrough the afternoon with some
OL,15,Fsunnier spells developing and showers
OL,16,Fbecoming fewer later. Breezy,
OL,17,Fespecially around coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
