OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FPatchy
OL,6,Fcloud developing on Sunday but mainly
OL,7,Fdry. A few showers on Monday but
OL,8,Fmostly dry by Tuesday. Winds lighter
OL,9,Fthan of late.
